OL,5, The government has confirmed a one-year
OL,6, suspension of the "triple lock" formula
OL,7, for annual state pension increases.    
OL,9,FThe move follows government concern    
OL,10,Fthat a big post-pandemic rise in       
OL,11,Faverage earnings would have meant      
OL,12,Fpensions increasing by 8%.             
OL,14,FWork and Pensions Secretary Therese    
OL,15,FCoffey said the average earnings       
OL,16,Fcomponent would be disregarded in the  
OL,17,F2022-23 financial year.                
OL,19,FInstead, the rise will be the consumer 
OL,20,Finflation rate or 2.5%.                
